      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVA LEANNE (2) has not raced for seven months. Looks forward enough for this return after a minor placing in a recent trial. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and is sure to have plenty of admirers. JILLIBY SAFFRON (1) produced a strong performance last time when she battled on bravely to just miss out over 1720m at Young. Tackles a similar assignment and she can take this out. ALABAMA LIONESS (3) came from the back row in a resuming fourth. Draws well and will be fitter so look for big improvement. TILLY DEEVINNE (8) finished ninth two runs ago then broke and finished a distant sixth over 1609m at Menangle at the latest appearance. Tactics will be crucial from this wide draw. Finds a nice race and can make up for that last start mishap.",
